{{IPAfont|⟨me<sub>2</sub>⟩}} → *{{IPAchar|[məj]}} → {{IPAchar|/me/|[me]}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|sort=め|-}}.<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref> Shift from ''ma'' above, formed through fusion of {{compound|ja|sort=め|目|tr1=ma|pos1=unbound form|い|tr2=i|pos2=emphatic nominal particle}}. Now the modern Japanese term for {{m|en|eye}}.

May also be cognate with {{m|ja|芽|tr=me||bud, shoot}},<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref> perhaps from the “visually prominent feature” sense.

